        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 27:15-26",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Deuteronomy 27:15-26",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Twelve curses against transgressions of the covenant. The first eleven are directed against special sins which are selected by way of example, the last comprehensively sums up in general terms and condemns all and every offence against God's Law. Compare the marginal references. ",
        "children": [
